    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 3,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 3 in World English Bible."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.1",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:1",
      "text": "Now these were the sons of David, who were born to him in Hebron: the firstborn, Amnon, of Ahinoam the Jezreelitess; the second, Daniel, of Abigail the Carmelitess;",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.2",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:2",
      "text": "the third, Absalom the son of Maacah the daughter of Talmai king of Geshur; the fourth, Adonijah the son of Haggith;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.3",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:3",
      "text": "the fifth, Shephatiah of Abital; the sixth, Ithream by Eglah his wife:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.4",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:4",
      "text": "six were born to him in Hebron; and he reigned there seven years and six months. He reigned thirty-three years in Jerusalem;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.5",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:5",
      "text": "and these were born to him in Jerusalem: Shimea, Shobab, Nathan, and Solomon, four, by Bathshua the daughter of Ammiel;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.6",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:6",
      "text": "and Ibhar, Elishama, Eliphelet,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.7",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:7",
      "text": "Nogah, Nepheg, Japhia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.8",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:8",
      "text": "Elishama, Eliada, and Eliphelet, nine.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.9",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:9",
      "text": "All these were the sons of David, in addition to the sons of the concubines; and Tamar was their sister.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.10",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:10",
      "text": "Solomon ’s son was Rehoboam, Abijah his son, Asa his son, Jehoshaphat his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.11",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:11",
      "text": "Joram his son, Ahaziah his son, Joash his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.12",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:12",
      "text": "Amaziah his son, Azariah his son, Jotham his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.13",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:13",
      "text": "Ahaz his son, Hezekiah his son, Manasseh his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.14",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:14",
      "text": "Amon his son, and Josiah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.15",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:15",
      "text": "The sons of Josiah: the firstborn Johanan, the second Jehoiakim, the third Zedekiah, and the fourth Shallum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.16",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:16",
      "text": "The sons of Jehoiakim: Jeconiah his son, and Zedekiah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.17",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:17",
      "text": "The sons of Jeconiah, the captive: Shealtiel his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.18",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:18",
      "text": "Malchiram, Pedaiah, Shenazzar, Jekamiah, Hoshama, and Nedabiah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.19",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:19",
      "text": "The sons of Pedaiah: Zerubbabel and Shimei. The sons of Zerubbabel: Meshullam and Hananiah; and Shelomith was their sister;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.20",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:20",
      "text": "and Hashubah, Ohel, Berechiah, Hasadiah, and Jushab Hesed, five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.21",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:21",
      "text": "The sons of Hananiah: Pelatiah and Jeshaiah; the sons of Rephaiah, the sons of Arnan, the sons of Obadiah, the sons of Shecaniah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.22",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:22",
      "text": "The son of Shecaniah: Shemaiah. The sons of Shemaiah: Hattush, Igal, Bariah, Neariah, and Shaphat, six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.23",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:23",
      "text": "The sons of Neariah: Elioenai, Hizkiah, and Azrikam, three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.3.24",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:24",
      "text": "The sons of Elioenai: Hodaviah, Eliashib, Pelaiah, Akkub, Johanan, Delaiah, and Anani, seven.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
